metadata.description:
The first-ever T1 NFT created draws inspiration from T1â€™s rich history and spirit of winning while celebrating the milestone of the T1 Dota 2 team's first qualification for The International. While this is just the start of the team's journey, there's only one first.

The NFT comes with a T1 Dota 2 team jersey fully autographed by all players. This is a once-off feature - once redeemed by the owner, it will not be available for subsequent redemption and when transacted to other owners.
metadata.name: T1 - The First
